        <h3 class="uk-h3 tm-heading-fragment">Column Highlight</h3>
        <a name="ColumnHighlight"></a>
        <p>Highlighting a column can be accomplished by adding a <code>class="highlight-col-1/2/3/4/5..."</code> to the to the table class.</p>

        <!-- Example -->
        <div class="uk-text-default uk-text-normal uk-text-uppercase">Example</div>
        <div class="uk-card uk-card-default uk-padding">
          <div class="basic-table">
